OL,3,CScottish university helps create
OL,4,Clateral flow tests from used chewing
OL,5,Cgum
OL,7,FA Scottish university has teamed up
OL,8,Fwith a moulding company to create
OL,9,Fmedical equipment from chewing gum
OL,10,Fscraped from the streets and old
OL,11,Ffridge components.
OL,13,FMaiwenn Kersaudy-Kerhoas, a professor
OL,14,Fin microfluidic engineering at Heriot-
OL,15,FWatt University, worked with English
OL,16,Fmoulding company Great Central
OL,17,FPlastics to develop lateral flow tests
OL,18,F(LFTs) in a project aimed at cutting
OL,19,Fmedical waste.
