OL,4,Clateral flow tests from used chewing
OL,5,Cgum
OL,7,FProf Kersaudy-Kerhoas has produced
OL,8,Ffive devices made from High Impact
OL,9,FPolystyrenes (HIPs), which are taken
OL,10,Ffrom a range of recycled plastics
OL,11,Fincluding "post-consumer" chewing gum
OL,12,Fand fridge parts.
OL,14,FIt is estimated that over four billion
OL,15,FLFTs are manufactured every year, with
OL,16,Faround 16,000 tonnes of plastic
OL,17,Fproduced globally each year for them.
OL,19,FThe tests check for a wide range of
OL,20,Fillnesses including strep A, pre-
OL,21,Feclampsia and Covid.
