OL,7,FProf Kersaudy-Kerhoas said that, if
OL,8,Fcreating LFTs from sustainable
OL,9,Fmaterials becomes the new norm, carbon
OL,10,Femissions can be cut by 30-80%.
OL,12,FShe said: "We've now had approval to
OL,13,Ftest these prototypes, making sure
OL,14,Fthey function as well as the existing
OL,15,Fones, particularly regarding the flow
OL,16,Fof liquid on the testing strip.
