OL,7,F"As well as demonstrating feasibility
OL,8,Fin their practical application, these
OL,9,Fnew devices help to support a wide-
OL,10,Franging discussion around healthcare
OL,11,Fsustainability in general and how we
OL,12,Fmight develop a circular economy
OL,13,Fthrough potential changes in
OL,14,Fprocurement and legislation.
OL,16,F"Sustainable plastics are not the only
OL,17,Fway, there are paper-based solutions
OL,18,Fin development, but they might take a
OL,19,Fwhile to be produced at scale, as
OL,20,Fmanufacturers will need significant
OL,21,Finvestment in new production lines.
