OL,7,F"After rigorous scientific, economical
OL,8,Fand regulatory investigations,
OL,9,Frecycled plastics could be used with
OL,10,Fexisting equipment and a quick win for
OL,11,Fsome products like LFTs."
OL,13,FSteve McLaughlin, deputy principal for
OL,14,Fresearch and impact at Heriot-Watt and
OL,15,Fthe director of health and care
OL,16,Ftechnologies, said: "Our researchers
OL,17,Fhere at Heriot-Watt University are
OL,18,Fworking hard to tackle climate change
OL,19,Fand finding new ways to reduce plastic
OL,20,Fwaste and the pollution it causes is
OL,21,Fpart of that.
