OL,7,F"Maiwenn and her team have been
OL,8,Fpassionate about reducing medical
OL,9,Fwaste throughout their careers and the
OL,10,Ffigures make it obvious why this is
OL,11,Fsuch an urgent issue.
OL,13,F"The mission of the new global
OL,14,Fresearch institute in health and care
OL,15,Ftechnologies is to work closely with
OL,16,Findustry and sector partners to
OL,17,Fdeliver innovative, sustainable and
OL,18,Fuse-inspired solutions to help solve
OL,19,Fglobal health challenges in a spirit
OL,20,Fof co-creation.
