OL,7,F"The work Maiwenn is doing on
OL,8,Fsustainable LFTs is exactly the sort
OL,9,Fof project we want to support and we
OL,10,Fhave the world-leading research and
OL,11,Fengineering capabilities here at
OL,12,FHeriot-Watt to do it."
OL,14,FGreat Central Plastics, based in
OL,15,FNorthamptonshire, specialises in
OL,16,Futilising recycled plastics.
